data.description: Welcome to this beautiful & private 4 bedroom, 31/2 bath home on an 1.18 acre. This home has an open custom kitchen & family room, separate living room, plus a master suite/guest room, down stairs. Upstairs is another large master suite with custom shower & bath, plus two large bedrooms & bath. The interior boasts numerous rooms, ensuring that everyone has their own personal space. The big backyard is perfect for outdoors activities and provides a tranquil retreat for relaxation. Take advantage to come see that house in person and discover all the features and amenities it has to offer. There is a nice large sunny backyard, perfect for a garden with room for kids to play and 2 sheds storage in the back. Schedule your showing today and experience the true beauty of this house this property.
